        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>STOP Straw Purchases Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes new criminal offenses and penalties to deter straw purchases of firearms (i.e., firearm purchases from a licensed gun dealer by one person on behalf of another person).</p>]]></text>
